Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna go there?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.06,0:00:04.02,2-f_01:01,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(983,1)}Class 2-F
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.56,0:00:05.77,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Got a minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:06.80,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.32,0:00:10.44,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to talk to you about \Nwhat to do on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.44,0:00:11.19,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.87,0:00:14.87,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, didn't you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.87,0:00:16.89,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking to Orimoto-san via email,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.89,0:00:18.68,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,and we decided to hang out on Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.68,0:00:20.45,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.65,0:00:24.60,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Then, want to come along?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.60,0:00:25.96,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.50,0:00:30.26,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Will you think of it as a favor to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.35,0:00:34.43,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be of any help to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.43,0:00:36.97,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the type who'd \Nneed help with that, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.66,0:00:40.22,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't want \Nto go out on a day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.80,0:00:43.98,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:53.49,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. Phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.77,0:00:54.96,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Whoa...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:00:57.40,Ore_Main,Komachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.40,0:00:58.99,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave it there when you're done.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.99,0:01:00.27,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.66,0:01:05.66,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.66,0:01:07.20,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Yahello!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.75,0:01:10.50,haruno_01:07,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinoshita Haruno
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.34,0:01:17.55,Show_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(235,1)}My Teen\NRomantic\NComedy\N{\c&H8D39E0&}SNAFU\N{\c&HDCA02E&}TOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.91,0:02:43.33,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Are you fighting with your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:45.93,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Not much of one, compared to you and yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.05,0:02:48.49,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I hear ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:50.07,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I heard the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.07,0:02:52.27,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You were invited on a date, \Nand you don't want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.32,0:02:55.16,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.16,0:02:58.39,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Hayato invited you. You should go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.39,0:02:59.87,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Um, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.87,0:03:04.06,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Aww... Hayato never bows his \Nhead to ask favors, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:06.35,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,He's got more pride than you'd think.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.88,0:03:12.29,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help wondering why he went \Nthat far to try to bring you along.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.34,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.34,0:03:18.05,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be romantic to go on \Na date with your old love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.48,0:03:22.72,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't call that "love."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:25.01,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,What wouldn't you call "love"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:29.27,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I was just pushing my own desires onto her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:32.60,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It was a mistake. \NI couldn't call it the real deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.94,0:03:38.59,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You're like some kind of logic \Nmonster, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.59,0:03:41.45,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean? \NIt's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.45,0:03:44.62,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Okay... Then you're a \Nself-consciousness monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.59,0:03:50.60,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway! You're going on the date!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.60,0:03:53.09,Ore_Italics,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't, I'll come to \Nyour house and drag you out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:01.68,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to have you come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.09,0:04:04.51,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I only came because Yukinoshita's \Nsister scares me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:06.55,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Thank her, not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.90,0:04:09.35,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,And why'd you move this to a \Nweekday just to get me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.35,0:04:10.97,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, isn't that them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.82,0:04:13.23,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry we're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.06,0:04:16.23,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:22.14,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Were we going to a movie first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:24.56,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I want to see a movie!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.56,0:04:26.02,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go see one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.02,0:04:27.38,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,What genre should we go for?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.38,0:04:29.08,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... Romance?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.08,0:04:29.91,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:41.87,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I'm seeing a movie with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.87,0:04:45.37,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,If I told the girls from middle \Nschool about this, they'd freak!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:46.26,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.26,0:04:47.33,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Totally!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:58.65,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Looking back, I feel like this is \Nhow it was in middle school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:03.78,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,We never once got any closer to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:10.16,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Orimoto Kaori just acts this way toward \Npeople she has no interest in, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.61,0:05:12.35,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's all it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:19.26,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Now, I finally feel like I managed \Nto end something that never started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:24.53,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that explosion \Nwas really huge, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.53,0:05:26.60,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Hikigaya jumped out of his skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:29.03,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,The way he was moving was so \Ncreepy, it was hilarious!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.03,0:05:30.85,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it was louder than I expected...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.22,0:05:33.16,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it startled me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.16,0:05:36.02,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,Buy Hayama-kun, you were \Ntotally calm, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.93,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I thought the same thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.93,0:05:42.51,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I jumped a little, but Hayama-kun \Ndidn't even flinch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:43.36,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.36,0:05:45.11,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,The way Hikigaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.37,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.51,0:05:51.87,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I hope my antics amused you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:55.53,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,We should hurry, or we won't \Nhave time to hit the stores.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.00,0:06:11.90,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Ebina, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.93,0:06:20.06,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Hayat—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.84,0:06:26.68,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Panties! Pink! Unexpected!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.47,Ore_Main,Hina,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Yumiko, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.87,0:06:32.74,Ore_Main,Yumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Haya...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.79,0:06:35.63,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,We should be going.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.63,0:06:36.33,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.75,0:06:40.37,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I want to check out the snowboarding gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.81,0:06:44.04,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is that Hayato-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.10,0:06:49.01,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Dude, Hayato-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.01,0:06:50.20,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.20,0:06:53.52,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to this! Irohas wanted a new tracksuit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.52,0:06:56.49,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,so we came to buy one, but all \Nwe've seen is protein stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.57,0:06:59.44,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Uh... Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:03.48,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Did I interrupt? My bad! We'll leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:04.59,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Irohas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.23,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:10.40,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're fast! Irohas, you're fast! Scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.65,0:07:13.01,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,What brings you here, Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:16.65,somenerve_07:10,Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(3885,1)}You've got some nerve, playing around with girls instead of working.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.01,0:07:14.90,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Were you out to have some fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.90,0:07:16.66,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like that's what she really means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.18,0:07:19.33,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wouldn't say fun—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.92,0:07:22.50,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the girl, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.50,0:07:25.79,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Is she your girlfriend? Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.79,0:07:27.63,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,But there are two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:29.04,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,What's your relationship with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.04,0:07:31.35,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,She's scary! Irohas is scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.73,0:07:34.80,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,How can she sound so cold when \Nshe's smiling like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:36.64,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Iroha.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.99,0:07:38.43,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I dragged him out with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:40.87,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.87,0:07:43.93,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I was just killing time here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.93,0:07:45.63,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we hang out together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.63,0:07:49.19,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Irohas, let's get going, too, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.41,0:07:52.31,Ore_Main,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Irohas, let's go to Riding Sport!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:55.00,Ore_Main,Iroha,0000,0000,0000,,I'll pass. They have mostly \Nbaseball stuff, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.00,0:07:58.05,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I guess even Iroha lets \Nyou see her that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.05,0:07:58.94,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:01.77,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Iroha wants to look cute to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.33,0:08:04.08,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I think she wants to be liked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.61,0:08:06.84,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,So it's unusual for her to be her real self.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.28,0:08:09.60,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That would mean she can be herself
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:12.05,Ore_Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,around me because she doesn't \Nwant me to like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.98,0:08:15.84,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,So you liked her in middle school, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.84,0:08:17.70,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hey, don't you think this one's better?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.13,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.13,0:08:18.60,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Was that the type you liked?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.97,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I'm not sure... I like this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.90,0:08:19.95,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't expect that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:21.02,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:22.31,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}This one? Okay, I'll get this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.02,0:08:22.75,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't just Orimoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.15,0:08:25.99,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There were much quieter girls \Nand noisier girls that I l—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.36,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That were my type, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.81,0:08:31.37,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what you'd call a "type."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:34.79,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Just because it was true then \Ndoesn't make it true now, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:36.42,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:42.31,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,We've probably never really, \Ntruly liked anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.79,0:08:46.28,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,You and me both.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.86,0:08:50.42,Ore_Flashback,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,I actually think Ebina-san's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.42,0:08:53.19,Ore_Flashback,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Hayato-kun? Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.19,0:08:53.85,Ore_Flashback,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.85,0:08:54.77,Ore_Flashback,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:55.85,Ore_Flashback,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm saying nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:58.47,Ore_Flashback,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon! That's no fair, Hayato-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.47,0:09:00.33,Ore_Flashback,Tobe,0000,0000,0000,,Just give me an initial!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:04.77,Ore_Flashback,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Y.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.24,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I guess that's why I had the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.32,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.32,0:09:14.57,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.57,0:09:15.70,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to eat, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:17.03,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,Anything's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:18.70,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,What should we eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:22.45,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe... Saize?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:23.59,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.59,0:09:25.12,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You said anything was good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.06,0:09:29.39,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What? You don't like Saize? \NOr you don't like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.39,0:09:29.79,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Saize? Saize?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.07,0:09:32.30,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we probably don't \Nwant anything that heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.24,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,How about that café?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.30,0:09:34.80,yon-marc_09:32,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Yon-Marc Café
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.55,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,The food here is so good!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.55,0:09:39.54,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I know! It's awesome! And so trendy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.17,0:09:39.54,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so full.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.54,0:09:42.24,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right? Trust Hayama-kun \Nto pick a good one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.24,0:09:43.39,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.90,0:09:44.58,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to Saize...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.58,0:09:46.82,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa... You're going there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.82,0:09:48.91,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm... not, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.63,0:09:49.04,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.91,0:09:52.51,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, though, who suggests Saize?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:53.82,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.23,0:09:57.27,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,It took me ages to figure out what \Nhe was even talking about at first!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.42,0:09:58.04,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}I know what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.65,0:09:58.38,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:09:58.55,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.38,0:09:59.96,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad we came to this café.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.50,0:10:00.29,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:04.05,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it when people do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.20,0:10:12.85,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:14.46,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mean that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.89,0:10:17.22,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.85,0:10:22.92,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.92,0:10:24.42,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.42,0:10:25.96,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.38,0:10:31.03,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, they're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.56,0:10:36.69,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.31,0:10:39.70,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Hikki...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:43.95,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:45.66,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I called them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.25,0:10:53.50,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Hikigaya isn't the loser \Nyou two think he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.15,0:10:57.21,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,He's friends with girls who \Nare much cooler than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.80,0:11:02.39,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Could you stop making selfish comments \Nafter making only surface judgments?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:12.35,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.35,0:11:14.84,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.84,0:11:16.53,Ore_Main,Chika,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I'm going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.29,0:11:24.19,Ore_Main,Kaori,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:34.67,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I was told we were meeting \Nto discuss the election.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.86,0:11:37.05,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Election? The student council one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.49,0:11:47.06,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, actually, we thought we'd ask Hayato-kun \Nto run in the election... so we...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.06,0:11:47.93,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.46,0:11:50.15,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Putting Hayama in the running...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:52.94,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing strange about that choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.30,0:11:54.24,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.24,0:11:57.73,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I just wanted to do whatever I could.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.97,0:12:00.86,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.44,0:12:02.56,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Nee-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.56,0:12:05.53,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,So you're not going to be student \Ncouncil president, Yukino-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.73,0:12:08.70,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,And I was sure that's what you'd do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:17.22,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,The way you push things like that \Nonto others is just like Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:21.33,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,But maybe that's fine for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.52,0:12:25.22,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to do anything, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.99,0:12:28.22,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Someone else will always \Ndo it for you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.41,0:12:37.50,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:44.80,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,If there's nothing else \Nto discuss, I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.43,0:12:48.54,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Yukinon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:55.83,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you do that to Yukinoshita?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:58.63,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You even have to ask? It's just the usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:02.02,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That was too elaborate to say \Nyou were just messing with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.02,0:13:03.01,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.01,0:13:08.98,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I have a little sister myself, \Nso it's not like I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.19,0:13:14.02,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You understand everything, \Ndon't you, Hikigaya-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.17,0:13:19.66,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make that scary face.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.66,0:13:21.93,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honestly impressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:23.44,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Well, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:25.50,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You're so interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:29.01,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,You always try to read what's \Nbehind every word and action.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:32.03,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I kind of like that, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.42,0:13:37.71,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cute, like you're afraid \Neveryone has evil intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.71,0:13:40.36,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing interesting \Nabout someone who can handle
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:42.02,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,everything flawlessly, is there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:47.42,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I found out what I wanted to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.42,0:13:48.97,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll get going, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:51.32,Ore_Main,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,This is boring now, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.89,0:13:58.14,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get weird ideas like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.98,0:14:00.70,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,That wasn't my intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.41,0:14:04.01,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I only did what I wanted to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.74,0:14:07.81,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Including what you said to \NOrimoto and her friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.92,0:14:12.02,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You sure that was a good idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.02,0:14:14.97,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in a crappy mood now. \NI never want to do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:17.83,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Then you shouldn't have done it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.03,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Gonna sit down?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.62,0:14:31.35,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I've been thinking all this time
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.84,0:14:34.68,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,of how I can get back what I destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.05,0:14:35.88,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.53,0:14:39.26,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I put my hopes in you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.69,0:14:42.69,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I relied on you, \Neven though I knew how you were.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:46.16,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,And because of that, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:48.14,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.14,0:14:50.62,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,You need to realize how much you're worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.02,0:14:52.99,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,And so do the people around you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.98,0:14:56.41,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.76,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,But that's hard to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.38,0:15:01.80,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I'd done it better.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.87,0:15:05.00,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,But this was all I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:08.26,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,This is how you've always lived, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.32,0:15:13.47,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stop making \Nyourself a sacrifice?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.02,0:15:16.47,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't put me on your level.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.87,0:15:18.64,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sacrifice? That's bull.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.00,0:15:21.74,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,This is what's natural for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.57,0:15:24.40,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'm always alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.78,0:15:27.40,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,So what everyone else thinks \Ndoesn't mean a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:31.59,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever happens in front of me \Nhappens to me, and me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.15,0:15:34.13,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get weird ideas and try to butt in.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:37.16,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't the reason you help people
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:40.73,Ore_Main,Hayama,0000,0000,0000,,because you want someone to help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:45.71,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.28,0:15:48.23,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't force your disgusting \Nidea of sympathy onto me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:49.80,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your pity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:59.39,hikigaya_15:57,Text,0000,0000,0000,,Hikigaya
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.72,0:16:00.74,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.09,0:16:03.95,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you call it self-sacrifice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.32,0:16:07.64,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell would I sacrifice \Nmyself for any of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.55,0:16:12.66,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I didn't say it out loud, \NI had my own solid conviction.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:16.09,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The one conviction that I \Nshared with someone else,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.77,0:16:20.45,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,and now I've lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.76,0:16:28.09,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinoshita came to talk to me this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.44,0:16:31.19,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,She says she's entering the running \Nfor student council president.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.15,0:16:34.09,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.72,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Hikigaya, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.48,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.48,0:16:45.00,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking strictly of credentials, \Nshe's fit for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.88,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.88,0:16:51.44,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,When the teachers and everyone else \Nfinds out, they should be thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.44,0:16:53.65,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't told anyone yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.65,0:16:54.58,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.35,0:16:57.03,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,So let me ask you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.56,0:17:00.66,Ore_Main,Hira,0000,0000,0000,,Hikigaya, what will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.74,0:17:06.17,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinoshita.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.93,0:17:10.88,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You plan to announce your candidacy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.20,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:16.90,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.90,0:17:19.03,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,I was just about to discuss it with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.03,0:17:20.89,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't call that a discussion.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:23.42,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because of what your sister said?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:26.60,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing to do with it. \NThis is my decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.60,0:17:28.12,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Yukinon, will the club...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.12,0:17:29.09,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.62,0:17:32.50,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,This club isn't that demanding,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.95,0:17:36.17,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,and I understand the work that comes \Nwith being on the student council.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:38.12,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,It won't place much strain on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:39.99,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Objectively speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.48,0:17:42.26,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,my doing this was the best choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.02,0:17:46.11,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Even against Isshiki-san, I can win easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.70,0:17:47.61,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:51.59,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't mind doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.88,0:17:56.08,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That may be, but not trying \Nat all is also an option.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:58.97,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Are you talking about your own suggestion?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:00.35,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.61,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking that anything you say or do
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:06.52,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,will move the entire \Nstudent body is arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.45,0:18:11.61,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Then I just have to think of how \Nto do it with that in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:17.04,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,Thinking that everyone \Nconcerns themselves with you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.65,0:18:19.99,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,enough to hate you is overly self-conscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.85,0:18:26.08,Ore_Main,Yukino,0000,0000,0000,,You and I don't go about \Nthings the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.64,0:18:28.58,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.05,0:18:34.31,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I see... So that's what you're \Ngoing to do, Yukinon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.97,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.11,0:18:49.88,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Let's walk home together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:53.73,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,So Yukinon's
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.11,0:18:56.28,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,gonna run in the election, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:58.43,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:01.64,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.22,0:19:04.14,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll try it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:05.49,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.82,0:19:08.87,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Try... You mean you'll run, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.38,0:19:13.48,Ore_Main,HAchi,0000,0000,0000,,But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.48,0:19:16.46,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:22.48,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing that I can do at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:27.27,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,So I thought, on the other hand, \Nthat might be a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.27,0:19:28.90,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,"On the other hand"?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.90,0:19:30.27,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't make a selfish decision like—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.27,0:19:31.56,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It's not selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.72,0:19:35.65,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It's everyone else who's selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.52,0:19:39.37,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Have you thought this out?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.37,0:19:40.86,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:44.16,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I thought about it and realized \Nit's my only choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:50.38,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'm going to work hard myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:54.56,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I realized that I've always \Njust relied on you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.06,0:19:56.40,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:19:59.92,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.92,0:20:01.44,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.44,0:20:05.38,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,So you don't have to work that hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.38,0:20:06.98,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the only reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:11.44,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,If Yukinon becomes student \Ncouncil president,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:15.32,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,she'll be the best student council \Npresident the school's ever had.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:17.13,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be good for the school, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.89,0:20:21.84,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,But it would probably \Nbe the end of our club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.50,0:20:24.45,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,The club won't go anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.45,0:20:25.94,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,It will.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:28.77,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Just like with the cultural festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.77,0:20:33.48,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You know Yukinon only focuses \Non one thing at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.38,0:20:37.46,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:42.27,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I like this club.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.01,0:20:47.81,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I... like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.30,0:20:56.67,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, you know... \NEven if I end up as president,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.67,0:20:58.21,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I could just do whatever to get by,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.21,0:21:00.91,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,and then I'd be able to stay in the club.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.91,0:21:02.39,Ore_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, it's me we're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.79,0:21:05.35,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,People don't expect much of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:08.03,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:10.43,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat Yukinon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.37,0:21:14.97,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Yuiga—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:17.54,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'll be fine from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:19.01,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,S-See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.01,0:21:20.03,Ore_Main,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.19,0:21:25.39,Ore_Main,Yui,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye, Hikki.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.47,0:21:35.86,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a choice both Yukinoshita \Nand Yuigahama can live with,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.86,0:21:37.26,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.21,0:21:39.27,Ore_Italics,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:08.97,Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,And Then,\NYuigahama Yui Makes a Declaration.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.56,0:24:08.42,Next_Ep_Title,Title,0000,0000,0000,,#05 The Scent of Tea Doesn't Fill That Room Anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.38,0:23:40.49,Ore_Main_Top,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.49,0:23:43.66,Ore_Main_Top,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,Milano-style doria, peperoncino, \Nand the drink bar...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.66,0:23:45.19,Ore_Main_Top,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,And chicken wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.19,0:23:46.24,Ore_Main_Top,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.88,0:23:50.80,Ore_Main_Top,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what's great about Saize is the \Nreasonable prices and classic good taste!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.80,0:23:53.09,Ore_Main_Top,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Saize is the greatest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.09,0:23:55.45,Ore_Main_Top,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I'll have the focaccia \Nand the drink bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.45,0:23:56.74,Ore_Main_Top,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,Is that enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.74,0:23:59.81,Ore_Main_Top,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Sure. Focaccia is really good \Nwith sweet syrup on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.81,0:24:02.87,Ore_Main_Top,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That sounds delicious! \NI think I'll have that, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.87,0:24:04.18,Ore_Main_Top,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.18,0:24:06.92,Ore_Main_Top,Zai,0000,0000,0000,,Chorizo Prosciutto!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.92,0:24:08.42,Ore_Main_Top,Hachi,0000,0000,0000,,Is that a finishing move?!
